dict.string: Add Awesome icon in navigation menu: In the class attribute within your code, type the name of the icon. Examples: Home page Styled Text Photo album Blog Page Contact Form File Sharing Sitemap ______________________________________________________________________________ Social icons: in this theme you can show your favorite social link with the Awesome icons . Icons list: http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/ Examples: ______________________________________________________________________________ Customize MENU text in drop navigation: Open the HTML code/CSS panel and paste the code: #drop:after {content:"OPEN";} Hide text: #drop:after {content:"";}
